	"NPCFish.Desc.Fizz": "It looks at you with the intent of someone having something to sell.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.Gourmand": "You found many diverse crops bits and pieces inside this shell.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.Governor": "This lobster oversees the region it declared its home.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.Grandpa": "You feel a strange sense of pride when looking at it.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.Gunther": "Strangely, it looks like it knows a lot of things.",
	"NPCFish.Desc.Henchman": "Its spikes become spikier when you approach its home.",
